All Implemented Interfaces:

public class PathWrite extends Struct implements NativeResource

Layout


 struct PathWrite_t {
     PathHandle_t ulPath;
     EPropertyWriteType writeType();
     ETrackedPropertyError eSetError();
     void * pvBuffer;
     uint32_t unBufferSize;
     PropertyTypeTag_t unTag;
     ETrackedPropertyError eError();
     char * pszPath;
 }

  • Constructor Details

    • PathWrite

      public PathWrite(ByteBuffer container)
      Creates a PathWrite instance at the current position of the specified ByteBuffer container. Changes to the buffer's content will be visible to the struct instance and vice versa.

      The created instance holds a strong reference to the container object.
